OL,3,CBurrow's parents 'proud' as ceremony
OL,4,Cheralds start of new MND centre
OL,6,FRob Burrow's parents said he would be
OL,7,F"so proud" as they attended an
OL,8,Femotional ceremony at the site of a
OL,9,Fnew motor neurone disease centre being
OL,10,Fbuilt in his name.
OL,12,FWork started on the Rob Burrow Centre
OL,13,Ffor Motor Neurone Disease (MND), in
OL,14,FLeeds, on Monday ` less than 24 hours
OL,15,Fafter
OL,17,FBurrow, who was 41, was diagnosed with
OL,18,FMND in December 2019.
