OL,3,CBurrow's parents 'proud' as ceremony
OL,4,Cheralds start of new MND centre
OL,6,F"We've just plucked up the courage
OL,7,Fhaven't we? Because thats what he
OL,8,Fwould've wanted," she said.
OL,10,FFunded by the Leeds Hospitals Charity,
OL,11,Fthe new centre will be the first of
OL,12,Fits kind in Europe, to give people
OL,13,Fliving with MND the best quality of
OL,14,Flife.
OL,16,FAround #5.5m of the expected
OL,17,F#6.8million cost has been raised so
OL,18,Ffar, including millions from the first
OL,19,Ftwo Rob Burrow Leeds Marathons, held
OL,20,Fin 2023 and 2024.
