OL,3,CBurrow's parents 'proud' as ceremony
OL,4,Cheralds start of new MND centre
OL,6,FSupporters, including clinical staff,
OL,7,Ffundraisers, architects, patients and
OL,8,Ftheir families, attended the ground-
OL,9,Fbreaking ceremony at Seacroft Hospital.
OL,11,FThey were joined by Burrow's former
OL,12,Fteammate and fellow fundraiser, Kevin
OL,13,FSinfield.
OL,15,FThe centre is expected to take around
OL,16,Fa year to build.
OL,18,FMeanwhile .
OL,20,FMrs Burrow said she was "so proud" at
OL,21,Fthe response to his death.
