OL,3,CBurrow's parents 'proud' as ceremony
OL,4,Cheralds start of new MND centre
OL,6,F"He was such a lovely, lovely person
OL,7,Fanyone that met Rob would always say
OL,8,Fthat.. and we're doing him proud
OL,9,Faren't we?," she added.
OL,11,FBurrow's dad, Geoff, added: "He was
OL,12,Fjust so genuine. What you saw is what
OL,13,Fyou got with Rob.
OL,15,F"He didn't really like publicity
OL,16,Fbelieve it or not but he did it, and
OL,17,Fhe wants us to keep doing it."
