OL,3,CBurrow's parents 'proud' as ceremony
OL,4,Cheralds start of new MND centre
OL,6,FMr Burrow said he wished his son could
OL,7,Fhave seen the centre built before he
OL,8,Fdied but said "we will get it for him
OL,9,Fand for all the families with MND".
OL,11,F"I know he'd be smiling. He'd be
OL,12,Fthinking, keep checking on them, dad.
OL,13,FMake sure they keep digging," he added.
OL,15,F"But we don't have to check, we know
OL,16,Fthat when this is built, try and
OL,17,Fimagine what it's going to be like. I
OL,18,Fjust hope i see it."
